<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">August 9, 2002 | Pages 10 and 11</font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">OTHER STORIES BELOW<br>
<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><a href="#Raytheon">Raytheon</a><br>
<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><a href="#Bay">East Bay hotel workers</a><br>
<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><a href="#Amherst">University of Massachusetts-Amherst</a><br>
